{"tid":1662214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來世上真係有平行時空嘅存在","createTime":"2019-10-18T15:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T15:44:39.000Z","uid":317464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc08baf9ee7c6e25f5c6438831608ec32e97497f","tid":1662214,"uid":317464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"發生咗咁政治事件，本人一直都有了解。但一直都覺得講咗4 5個月應該冇平行時空嘅人㗎。咁啱身邊有個藍屍朋友突然喺群組喥放藍料，我頂唔撚順問佢知唔知一百萬人上街為咩。<br />\n佢嘅答案(本人毒撚)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSvuRP0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSvuRP0.jpg&h=1abe60ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌!連條條例叫咩名都唔知真係匪夷所思!<br />\n係佢，帶領咗我去另一個世界觀。真係有平行時空㗎!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8104d96d71d146246cf3d3e0f5150fa2c44b6a","tid":1662214,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"BG男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a155f5565eec2174db74d5463a2045685e17fd97","tid":1662214,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:39:39.000Z","msg":"【日常文宣】[推爆佢]本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1662234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1662234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"641ed0cd4e6a4351739aacc4e13b9c9ffa249d78","tid":1662214,"uid":317464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa8104d96d71d146246cf3d3e0f5150fa2c44b6a","tid":1662214,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"BG男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:41:54.000Z","msg":"女啊"},{"pid":"c5fbda56faec4cfb4006386ce1e722f81c845a51","tid":1662214,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"點解我睇唔明佢up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c